00:12:48,234 --> 00:12:50,270
Mycoskie:
I was born in Arlington, Texas,

00:12:50,270 --> 00:12:53,406
and grew up spending most of
my life practicing tennis.

00:12:53,406 --> 00:12:55,241
I wanted to be
a professional tennis player,

00:12:55,241 --> 00:12:58,411
but unfortunately, I had
a career‐ending injury

00:12:58,411 --> 00:13:02,382
that stopped my hopes
and dreams in the tennis world.

00:13:02,382 --> 00:13:03,683
My first business was

00:13:03,683 --> 00:13:05,718
a pickup‐and‐delivery
laundry service.

00:13:05,718 --> 00:13:07,987
The only reason
I became an entrepreneur

00:13:07,987 --> 00:13:10,890
was I had a need for someone
to come do my laundry

00:13:10,890 --> 00:13:12,425
because I was on crutches

00:13:12,425 --> 00:13:15,194
and couldn't carry my own
laundry down to the facility.

00:13:15,194 --> 00:13:16,996
I went from knowing
nothing about business

00:13:16,996 --> 00:13:20,967
to running a company in
three states with 40 employees.

00:13:20,967 --> 00:13:22,935
By the time I was 29 years old,

00:13:22,935 --> 00:13:25,638
I had created four businesses
and sold three of them.

00:13:25,638 --> 00:13:28,708
Frankly, I was a little bit
exhausted and burnt out,

00:13:28,708 --> 00:13:30,777
so I decided
to go to Argentina.

00:13:30,777 --> 00:13:32,645
When I was in Argentina
and traveling,

00:13:32,645 --> 00:13:34,280
one thing in particular
I witnessed

00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:37,350
was really intense poverty,
and that really stuck with me.

00:13:37,350 --> 00:13:39,686
Many of the children
were in the streets

00:13:39,686 --> 00:13:40,820
when they should be in school,

00:13:40,820 --> 00:13:42,855
and specifically,
not wearing shoes.

00:13:42,855 --> 00:13:45,758
That's when I had the idea
to create a shoe business

00:13:45,758 --> 00:13:47,827
where every time
we sold a pair of shoes,

00:13:47,827 --> 00:13:50,129
we would give a pair
to a child in need.

00:13:50,129 --> 00:13:51,497
We told them our vision,

00:13:51,497 --> 00:13:53,299
and they thought
we were totally crazy.

00:13:53,299 --> 00:13:55,835
Every business consultant
I talked to couldn't believe

00:13:55,835 --> 00:13:58,938
that I was gonna give something
away every time I sold it.

00:13:58,938 --> 00:14:00,707
But because it was so radical,

00:14:00,707 --> 00:14:03,042
it differentiated us
and allowed us to become

00:14:03,042 --> 00:14:05,845
one of the fastest‐growing
shoe companies in the world.

00:14:05,845 --> 00:14:08,247
Today, there are
thousands of companies

00:14:08,247 --> 00:14:10,616
who have either emulated
the one‐for‐one model

00:14:10,616 --> 00:14:13,086
or created a social cause
in their business.

00:14:13,086 --> 00:14:17,357
To date, Toms has now
donated over 96 million shoes

00:14:17,357 --> 00:14:18,825
to children around the world,

00:14:18,825 --> 00:14:22,161
and we had reached sales
over $500 million a year.

00:14:22,161 --> 00:14:24,297
After growing Toms
for eight years

00:14:24,297 --> 00:14:25,965
and dedicating my life to it,

00:14:25,965 --> 00:14:28,868
I realized I wanted to do more
as an entrepreneur,

00:14:28,868 --> 00:14:32,338
and so I sold half
of the company in 2014.

00:14:32,338 --> 00:14:35,241
Making small changes
in our lives

00:14:35,241 --> 00:14:36,776
can truly transform them.

00:14:36,776 --> 00:14:39,479
This led me on
a two‐year pilgrimage

00:14:39,479 --> 00:14:42,315
to meet some of the top
scientists in our country

00:14:42,315 --> 00:14:44,951
on the state of well‐being
and really thriving.

00:14:44,951 --> 00:14:47,820
This experience led to me
launching a new company,

00:14:47,820 --> 00:14:49,055
called Madefor.

00:14:49,055 --> 00:14:50,390
Our hope with Madefor

00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:53,126
is to teach everyone habits
and practices

00:14:53,126 --> 00:14:55,161
that can truly transform
their lives

00:14:55,161 --> 00:14:57,430
and help all of us
answer the question

00:14:57,430 --> 00:14:58,965
"What am I made for?"

00:15:00,166 --> 00:15:02,101
One of the things
I'm most excited about

00:15:02,101 --> 00:15:04,070
is competing
with the other Sharks.

00:15:04,070 --> 00:15:06,472
Most people know me
as this do‐gooder,

00:15:06,472 --> 00:15:08,341
but I'm really competitive.

00:15:08,341 --> 00:15:11,677
Success to me means feeling
that you've done your best

00:15:11,677 --> 00:15:14,981
to make the greatest impact
you can while on this planet,

00:15:14,981 --> 00:15:19,685
knowing that you have given life
everything you can

00:15:19,685 --> 00:15:21,354
and you've held nothing back.

