00:16:11,370 --> 00:16:12,939
in your electric vehicle.

00:16:12,939 --> 00:16:15,708
That's why I would love
to introduce you to the Roadie,

00:16:15,708 --> 00:16:17,176
the world's first
and only

00:16:17,176 --> 00:16:20,079
portable, modular,
and ultrafast EV charger.

00:16:20,079 --> 00:16:22,782
The anxiety of finding
a charging station

00:16:22,782 --> 00:16:26,085
and the time wasted waiting
for a vehicle to charge

00:16:26,085 --> 00:16:27,954
simply goes away
when the charging station

00:16:27,954 --> 00:16:30,056
comes to <i>you,</i>
no matter where you are.

00:16:30,056 --> 00:16:31,858
The Roadie has
three core features.

00:16:31,858 --> 00:16:33,826
Number one ‐‐ modularity.

00:16:33,826 --> 00:16:35,394
Units can be
connected together

00:16:35,394 --> 00:16:36,929
to give
the electric vehicle owner

00:16:36,929 --> 00:16:38,664
the exact amount of range
they want.

00:16:38,664 --> 00:16:40,299
