a charging station.

00:16:47,306 --> 00:16:49,976
And, of course, the most
important factor ‐‐ speed.

00:16:49,976 --> 00:16:51,644
We can charge
an electric vehicle

00:16:51,644 --> 00:16:54,447
at a rate
of one mile every 60 seconds.

00:16:54,447 --> 00:16:57,116
So, Sharks, help us create
a more sustainable

00:16:57,116 --> 00:16:59,118
